        "liquid": "<style>\n.tp-reviews {\n  padding: 80px 20px;\n  background: #fff;\n  text-align: center;\n  font-family: inherit;\n}\n.tp-wrapper {\n  position: relative;\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 0 50px;\n}\n.tp-overflow {\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.tp-track {\n  display: flex;\n  transition: transform 0.4s ease;\n  gap: 24px;\n}\n.tp-card {\n  min-width: calc(33.333% - 16px);\n  max-width: calc(33.333% - 16px);\n  background: #fff;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\n  overflow: hidden;\n  text-align: left;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n}\n.tp-card img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 280px;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  display: block;\n}\n.tp-body { padding: 24px; }\n.tp-stars {\n  color: #f5a623;\n  font-size: 1.15rem;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n}\n.tp-title {\n  font-size: 1.15rem;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #1a1a3e;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  line-height: 1.35;\n}\n.tp-text {\n  font-size: 0.92rem;\n  color: #666;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  margin-bottom: 22px;\n}\n.tp-footer {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\n  padding-top: 16px;\n}\n.tp-author {\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1a1a3e;\n  font-size: 0.95rem;\n}\n.tp-badge {\n  background: #e8f5e9;\n  color: #2e7d32;\n  font-size: 0.75rem;\n  padding: 5px 12px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 4px;\n}\n.tp-btn {\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 42%;\n  transform: translateY(-50%);\n  background: #e8632a;\n  color: white;\n  border: none;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  width: 48px;\n  height: 48px;\n  font-size: 1.3rem;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  z-index: 10;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(232,99,42,0.4);\n  transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;\n}\n.tp-btn:hover {\n  background: #c95020;\n  transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.08);\n}\n.tp-btn.prev { left: 0; }\n.tp-btn.next { right: 0; }\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .tp-card { min-width: 100%; max-width: 100%; }\n  .tp-btn.prev { left: 0; }\n  .tp-btn.next { right: 0; }\n  .tp-wrapper { padding: 0 30px; }\n}\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"tp-reviews\">\n  <div class=\"tp-wrapper\">\n    <button class=\"tp-btn prev\" onclick=\"tpMove(-1)\">&#8592;</button>\n    <div class=\"tp-overflow\">\n      <div class=\"tp-track\" id=\"tpTrack\">\n\n        <div class=\"tp-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0770/2016/8389/files/Sans_titre_Logo_-3.jpg?v=1772735210\" alt=\"avis client chat\">\n          <div class=\"tp-body\">\n            <div class=\"tp-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-title\">Chat beaucoup plus calme et heureux</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-text\">Une amie me l'a recommandé et je suis tellement contente d'avoir essayé ! Mon chat faisait ses besoins partout, mais ça a super bien marché. Il est tellement plus calme et mes chats s'entendent enfin !</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-footer\">\n              <span class=\"tp-author\">Mélissa N.</span>\n              <span class=\"tp-badge\">✔ Achat Vérifié</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"tp-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0770/2016/8389/files/cat5.webp?v=1772734967\" alt=\"avis client chat\">\n          <div class=\"tp-body\">\n            <div class=\"tp-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-title\">Je n'en revenais pas que ça marche aussi bien.</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-text\">J'allais presque en faire un chat d'extérieur à cause des marquages urinaires. Après une semaine avec le diffuseur, les marquages ont complètement arrêté !</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-footer\">\n              <span class=\"tp-author\">Donna C.</span>\n              <span class=\"tp-badge\">✔ Achat Vérifié</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"tp-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0770/2016/8389/files/Sans_titre_Logo_-2.jpg?v=1772734963\" alt=\"avis client chat\">\n          <div class=\"tp-body\">\n            <div class=\"tp-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-title\">Ça a vraiment fonctionné !</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-text\">Mes chats se battaient tout le temps — sifflements, grognements, attaques. J'ai essayé d'autres diffuseurs sans résultat. Celui-ci a tout changé ! Ils sont tellement plus calmes maintenant.</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-footer\">\n              <span class=\"tp-author\">Patricia S.</span>\n              <span class=\"tp-badge\">✔ Achat Vérifié</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"tp-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0770/2016/8389/files/Sans_titre_Logo_-3.jpg?v=1772735210\" alt=\"avis client chat\">\n          <div class=\"tp-body\">\n            <div class=\"tp-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-title\">Résultats visibles dès 48h !</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-text\">Mon chat était très anxieux lors des orages et des visites. Depuis Therapattes, il reste calme et n'a plus peur de rien. Je ne m'y attendais pas si vite !</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-footer\">\n              <span class=\"tp-author\">Sophie M.</span>\n              <span class=\"tp-badge\">✔ Achat Vérifié</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"tp-card\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0770/2016/8389/files/cat5.webp?v=1772734967\" alt=\"avis client chat\">\n          <div class=\"tp-body\">\n            <div class=\"tp-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-title\">Le meilleur investissement pour mon chat</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-text\">Mon vétérinaire me l'a conseillé et c'est la meilleure décision que j'ai prise. Mon chat ronronne à nouveau et est complètement apaisé !</div>\n            <div class=\"tp-footer\">\n              <span class=\"tp-author\">Julie R.</span>\n              <span class=\"tp-badge\">✔ Achat Vérifié</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"tp-btn next\" onclick=\"tpMove(1)\">&#8594;</button>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<script>\nvar tpIndex = 0;\nvar tpTotal = 5;\nvar tpTrack = document.getElementById('tpTrack');\nfunction tpMove(dir) {\n  var vis = window.innerWidth <= 768 ? 1 : 3;\n  var max = tpTotal - vis;\n  tpIndex += dir;\n  if (tpIndex < 0) tpIndex = 0;\n  if (tpIndex > max) tpIndex = max;\n  var w = tpTrack.children[0].offsetWidth + 24;\n  tpTrack.style.transform = 'translateX(-' + (tpIndex * w) + 'px)';\n}\n</script>",
